# Generate QR

This end point return a qr in base64 format

## Request

| End Point | **/generateQR**                   |
| --------- | --------------------------------- |
| Method    | GET                               |
| Params:   | meetingId=_<string>_              |
| Headers:  | Content-Type:application/json     |
|           | Authorization:Bearer _<token_id>_ |

## Response

Example:

```json
{
  "data": "data:image/png;base64,"
}
```
